## Verification + policy

### Verification defaults
- Cheap default: `pnpm test` (Vitest only)
- Full pre-handoff: `pnpm verify:full`
- Run browser suites only when explicitly needed:
  - `pnpm test:e2e`
  - `pnpm test:release-smoke`

If you cannot run expected verification, say exactly what was not run and why.

### Lockfile policy
GitHub Actions owns `pnpm-lock.yaml`.
- Do not commit `pnpm-lock.yaml` in pull requests.

